rComments: Her lectures are dry. Her content is relatively easy to master. Lot of memorization. She doesnt face the audience when she talks hence not a very confident speaker. I did well in my midterms and final. The only thing concerning is why are required lab readings tested on the final exam. its counter intuitive which doesn't make it cohesive.
